msgid "TUI API"
msgstr ""

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/tui.md:3
msgid "Terminal UI helpers are available under `ptool.tui` and `p.tui`."
msgstr ""

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/tui.md:5
msgid ""
"The first version focuses on small interactive terminal screens driven by a "
"Lua event loop."
msgstr ""

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/tui.md:8
msgid "ptool.tui.run"
msgstr ""

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/tui.md:10
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/tui.md:10"
msgid "`Unreleased` - Introduced."
msgstr ""

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/tui.md:12
msgid ""
"`ptool.tui.run(options)` starts a TUI session, runs the Lua lifecycle "
"callbacks, and returns the value passed to `app:quit(value)`. If `app:quit()`"
" is called without a value, the function returns `nil`."
msgstr ""

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/tui.md:16
msgid "`options` fields:"
msgstr ""

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/tui.md:18
msgid ""
"`tick_ms` (integer, optional): Tick interval in milliseconds. Defaults to "
"`100`."
msgstr ""

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/tui.md:20
msgid ""
"`init` (function, optional): Called once before the first frame is drawn. "
"Its return value becomes the initial `state`."
msgstr ""

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/tui.md:22
msgid ""
"`update` (function, required): Called as `update(state, event, app)` after "
"each input event or tick. If it returns a non-`nil` value, that value "
"becomes the next `state`. Returning `nil` keeps the current `state`."
msgstr ""

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/tui.md:25
msgid ""
"`view` (function, required): Called as `view(state, app)` to build the root "
"node for the next frame."
msgstr ""

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/tui.md:28
msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr ""

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/tui.md:30
msgid "Requires an interactive TTY."
msgstr ""

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/tui.md:31
msgid "Runs inside the terminal alternate screen with raw mode enabled."
msgstr ""

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/tui.md:32
msgid "Restores the terminal when the session exits, including error paths."
msgstr ""

