#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/tui.md:138
msgid "`ptool.tui.list(items[, options])` creates a vertical list node."
msgstr ""

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/tui.md:140
msgid ""
"`items` (table, required): A dense list table. Item values may be strings, "
